As students compare swag items like water bottles and phone chargers, announcement chimes signal the final hour of the event.

A robotics startup flies a small drone above its booth for attention. Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths. Career counselors remind attendees to maintain eye contact as students exit the venue carrying tote bags and stacks of business cards, while recruiters encourage them to follow up with personalized emails. Simultaneously, workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom. Career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops.

A welcome announcement outlining the fair schedule is broadcast over the PA system. Meanwhile, volunteers stack collapsed booths and gather leftover brochures. As the day winds down, interview sign-up sheets fill with names, and recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails.
